Quote: He had a hunk of wood in his hand and a pocket knife - the wood to hit it over the head and the pocket-knife to bleed it once it was down. Only it wasn't a 50 pound porker, but a very angry full-grown boar which at that moment left the dogs and came galloping up the hill.
